br />\n另外 唔講條片係咪racist 個主持同條片亦都完全唔好笑 好多位都好夾硬 睇到勁尷尬 <br />\n夾硬製造啲低級趣味出嚟話咩條嘢&ldquo;係正常嘅四倍 中國人嗰啲都好細碌&rdquo; 然後又話咩&ldquo;呢個係暗示 唔好意思 係暗示&rdquo; 睇完真係心諗做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瑞典片嗰條高質過佢n倍 <br />\n<br />\n樓上班戇鳩唔好見到人哋笑鳩支那就幫人奶袋底先得架<br />\n睇佢拉埋日本嚟講 就知班意大利佬戇鳩嘅程度拍得住支那人 自大程度有過之而無不及</blockquote>"},{"pid":"58e8d3cf8e2cf2a66a87085d1e6e2292910b354e","tid":916681,"uid":12269,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://starecat.com/content/wp-content/uploads/googling-italian-ww2-weapon-factory-pasta-machine.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstarecat.com%2Fcontent%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fgoogling-italian-ww2-weapon-factory-pasta-machine.jpg&h=33b2a1a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54d6267c728ee20adf002a90898bffabecf275d7","tid":916681,"uid":28163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:01:17.000Z","msg":"Mao-fia 呢個好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505312ad35aead70af9a85f23ea2e5ec7ec152c0","tid":916681,"uid":54226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:01:31.000Z","msg":"五毛出哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f5099f1fb06b5df20a9a932a4e8955d70e1fd7","tid":916681,"uid":28163,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69d887467b508c0e0738eae4f48d0faaa2042bdb","tid":916681,"uid":12498,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:17:02.000Z","msg":"中國人真係最鐘意夾埋外人笑自人，5000年都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"行撚開啦你<br />\n香港人會食狗嫁<br />\n報警拉鳩你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d94ead6cc1bebb4a1ebc4587ddae4f9d80c9272","tid":916681,"uid":30384,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f9f5099f1fb06b5df